    },
    {
      "agency": "City of Garden Grove / OCFA",
      "time_iso": "2026-05-30T21:00:00Z",
      "text": "The safety zone around the involved tank has been reduced to 150 feet due to continued stabilization of conditions. All roads that were closed as a result of the hazardous materials incident are now open.",
